From: JS Lemay <js.lemay@mq.edu.au>

From: JS Lemay <js.lemay@mq.edu.au>
Sent: Tuesday, October 24, 2023 4:13 PM
To: Categories mailing list <categories@mq.edu.au>
Subject: [Categories]: Publication of Volume LXIV-4 of the Cahiers

[[JSPL: The following email was sent to the old mailing list by ehres@u-picardie.fr<mailto:ehres@u-picardie.fr> while it was offline]]

Dear Colleagues,

We are pleased to inform you that Volume LXIV-4 (4th quarter 2023) of the
Cahiers is now freely downloadable from the website of the Cahiers:
http://cahierstgdc.com<http://cahierstgdc.com>

both as a whole issue and as separate articles.

Best regards,
Andree Ehresmann, Marino Gran and Rene Guitar
